import { Container, Typography, Box, Button, Grid, Card, CardContent } from '@mui/material'; import { KeyboardArrowRight, Speed, LocalGasStation, Timer, Star } from '@mui/icons-material'; function Home() { const features = [ { icon: , title: "Affordable", value: "Great Prices" }, { icon: , title: "Efficient", value: "Low Running Costs" }, { icon: , title: "Finance", value: "Easy Terms" }, { icon: , title: "Rating", value: "4.8/5.0" } ]; // Update price ranges and descriptions to match low/mid range const featuredCars = [ { name: "Ford Focus 1.0 EcoBoost", price: "£12,995", image: "https://m.atcdn.co.uk/a/media/w800h600/a75d2f3d4f464986a92c5e3c4f4c24c5.jpg", description: "2020 • 30k miles • Petrol" }, { name: "Vauxhall Corsa SRi", price: "£11,495", image: "https://m.atcdn.co.uk/a/media/w800h600/583e4d3c5c6745dfa3b62036af943537.jpg", description: "2021 • 25k miles • Petrol" }, { name: "VW Golf Match", price: "£13,995", image: "https://m.atcdn.co.uk/a/media/w800h600/20f8f36d0f8a4ddba6c87e40c8268c4a.jpg", description: "2019 • 35k miles • Petrol" } ]; return ( {/* Hero Section - Updated content */} Quality Cars
Affordable Prices Find your perfect car with flexible finance options and exceptional service. {/* About Us Section - New */} About Us Welcome to [Showroom Name], your trusted local car dealership serving the community since 2010. We specialize in quality used cars and affordable new vehicles, making car ownership accessible to everyone. Our team of experienced professionals is dedicated to helping you find the perfect car that fits both your needs and budget. We offer competitive finance options and outstanding after-sales service. 1000+ Happy Customers 500+ Cars Sold 4.8 Average Rating {/* Features Section */} {features.map((feature, index) => ( {feature.icon} {feature.title} {feature.value} ))} {/* Featured Cars Section */} Featured Models {featuredCars.map((car, index) => ( {car.name} {car.price} {car.description} ))} ); } export default Home;
